# ORIG TITLE    Europe’s biggest hashish seizure made in Spain . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Spanish police have made Europe’s biggest-ever seizure of hashish, just days after the country saw another record haul of cannabis. 52 tonnes of the drug were found in 1,700 packets at a warehouse in Cordoba in the south of the country. Three people have been arrested near Huelva and Seville as the police operation continued on Monday. The alarm was raised by a haulier who had been tied up and gagged when he turned up at the warehouse. 
